commit.title: [toplevel] Move compilation-related functions to their own module.
commit.message:
[toplevel] Move compilation-related functions to their own module.

We move compilation-specific functions to their own module. This is a
first step in maybe separating `coqtop` from `coqc`. In the current
situation `coqtop` acts as both a shell and a compiler, with the
consequent obfuscation of code.

cc: #8683
